<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Hidden Valley</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1990, the Hidden Valley is bound by the Shaganappi Trail on the west, the Country Hills Boulevard on the south, the Stoney Trail on the north and the Beddington Trail on the east.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Hidden Valley from starter homes and townhomes to the more lavish bungalows with elaborate structures and backyard ponds! </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average cost for a single-family detached home in the neighborhood is in the $410,000 price range. </p>
